data.text:
Bleeding Through

Regina casts a spell in hope of finding out why Zelena was abandoned; Belle discovers what Zelena's ultimate goal is.

The Miller's Daughter

Cora and Regina try to overpower Mr. Gold; dark magic tempts Mary Margaret; Rumplestiltskin offers his services to Cora.

Enigma

Sean tries unusual methods to cure his insomnia; Christian and Kimber go into business together; Liz confronts Christian, and gives Kimber some unsolicited advice.

Abigail Sullivan

Matt's crime sprees catch up to him; Julia returns from New York; Sean discovers devastating details about his marriage to Teddy.
